Print the following pattern
Pattern for N = 4
( You can see the question on the coding ninjas site )

The dots represent spaces.



Input Format :
N (Total no. of rows)
Output Format :
Pattern in N lines
Sample Input :
5
Sample Output :


The dots represent spaces.


Solution-

#include<iostream>
using namespace std;


int main(){

       /*  Read input as specified in the question.
	* Print output as specified in the question.
	*/
    int x,n;
    cin>>n;
    for(int i=1;i<=n;i++)
    {
        x=i;
		for(int j=1;j<=n-i;j++)
        {
            cout<<" ";
        }
        for(int k=1;k<=i;k++)
        {
            cout<<x++;
        }
        cout<<endl;
    
    }
  
}
